FROM python:3.11-slim AS base

WORKDIR /app

# Install system dependencies
RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends \
    libgomp1 \
    && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*

# Stage 1: Install Python dependencies (cached layer)
FROM base AS dependencies

COPY requirements.txt .

RUN pip install --no-cache-dir --index-url https://download.pytorch.org/whl/cpu \
    torch --target=/app/deps && \
    pip install --no-cache-dir \
    fastapi \
    uvicorn[standard] \
    opencv-python-headless \
    numpy \
    scikit-learn \
    --target=/app/deps

# Stage 2: Download model (cached layer)
FROM dependencies AS model-builder

COPY download_model.py .

RUN python download_model.py

# Stage 3: Final runtime image
FROM base

# Copy dependencies
COPY --from=dependencies /app/deps /usr/local/lib/python3.11/site-packages

# Copy downloaded model
COPY --from=model-builder /app/model.pt .

# Copy application code (changes frequently - last layer)
COPY . .

EXPOSE 8000

CMD ["uvicorn", "main:app", "--host", "0.0.0.0", "--port", "8000"]
